Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have as horrible\Na reputation as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. I am a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Arlong's a reasonable guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more until our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I'm going\Nto earn 100 million Berries
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and buy this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Usopp Dead?! When is Luffy\NGoing to Make Landfall?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! To Arlong Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have they still not caught\Nthat Long-nose yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mere, lowly human,\Ndefying our species!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're returning to Arlong Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't lose 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who thinks Usopp-sama is too\Nimportant of a person to have die yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me! Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys think so, too? I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack: Egg Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Rotten eggs!\N--I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Howdya like that?! I guess fishmen\Naren't all they're cracked up to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like every one of 'em\Nlet Captain Usopp escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yikes. I somehow\Nwound up at a shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I heard his voice over here!\N--Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one here.\NWas it just our imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy's quick to run away,\Nthat's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not in your best interest to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your cheering!\NAs you can see, I'm perfectly okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a little too okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking so long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When is Luffy gonna show up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five more minutes\Nand I'm gonna die of boredom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even Hatchan, major octopus\Nleader of the Arlong Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can pull you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a super-grade fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno who you are, but you're\Nthe gutsiest fish in the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... Oh! It was me all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're indeed the gutsiest\Nfish in the East Blue, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, does that seem strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I'm Hatchan! Call me Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You a fishman, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, of course!\NI'm a fascinating octopus fishman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the looks of it, you're a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A marine? Or maybe a guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say I'm a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san's not here right now, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, there's a long-nosed\Noutsider running all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He locked up his friend here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and went to Cocoyashi Village\Nto get this other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll save him for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Cocoyashi Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How do I get there?\N--Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a guest.\NI'll take you there, swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my brothers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What are you trying to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate hunter?!\NDid he come to collect my head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, he didn't come... T-That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He was Zoro!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That haramaki guy\Nwe caught was Roronoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught him, Arlong-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What in the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough, Choo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me Zoro--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cocoyashi Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! Bye, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! I just remembered,\NI forgot to ask your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me? What are you\Nasking my name again for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hatchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catching this scum isn't\Nenough to satisfy my hunger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, huh?! So you should let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just saying hello earlier!\NT-That's how we do it in my village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you are one of Zoro's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, it's only natural for famous\Nbounty hunters to come after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kill me! I don't have\Nanything to do with Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your poor lies.\NYou stood up to Arlong-san, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like you're\Ngoing to live either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:10:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! As a matter of fact,\NZoro and I are really close!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So just try and lay a finger on me!\NZoro won't stand by quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Which means if I kill you,\NZoro will come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing me'd be very bad!\NIf you keep me alive, Zoro'll show up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't keep me alive,\NZoro won't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how exactly did Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...escape from our prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is, someone let him escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san. Does this\Nsound plausible to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps Nami let Zoro infiltrate\Nthis place so he could take your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now that you mention it,\NNami has been acting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She even helped Zoro\Nwhen he jumped into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she was working\Nwith Zoro from the very start...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and tricked us all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Betrayal is her specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.09,0:11:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit discussing stuff based\Non a bunch of conjecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, a traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore I was a member of this group\Neight years ago, with this tattoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.33,0:11:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami. It's only natural\Nfor you to be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But rest easy.\NI don't suspect you one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and me've known each\Nother for eight years now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just a little on edge is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones we do need to get rid of\Nare Roronoa Zoro and his group!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Nami! S-Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro just had to go and do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem a little pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as for Long-nose here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not even you can save him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not after he's defied Arlong-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to suspect me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too smart, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the amount\NArlong and I agreed to soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I betray you now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed amount?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You agreed eight years ago to buy\NCocoyashi Village from Arlong-san
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for 100 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I just can't make sense of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You betrayed the villagers\Nand your parent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and only trust money,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so why do you care so much\Nabout Cocoyashi Village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why such a puny little village?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.99,0:13:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I found this... in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Say what?! Usopp's been captured?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They took him to\NArlong Park a little while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brave as he was,\Nthat youngster defied Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's surely dead by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all times to get caught, it had\Nto be after I killed some time there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:14:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Stay alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a treasure map?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be pointing\Nto Cocoyashi Village...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Treasure in Cocoyashi Village?!\N--Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my own personal map!\NIt has nothing to do with you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.39,0:14:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! What's wrong?\NYou suddenly look so furious...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the work of Roronoa Zoro,\Nthe pirate hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where were you, Hachi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could've been prevented,\Nhad you been here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it could've!\NHad I only been here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning you don't know\Nwhere Zoro disappeared to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.89,0:15:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all I saw was one\Nslightly suspicious swordsman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whom I'd never met before...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did see him, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where did Zoro go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to see Arlong-san,\Nso I just took him to Cocoyashi Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning there's no reason\Nto rush out in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking for me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was a guest\Nof yours, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.53,0:15:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I didn't think you'd be\Nback so soon, Arlong-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, if I can just\Nbuy me a little more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting in the way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's so close to working out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So close!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn you! You picking a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting in the way!\NYou're the one to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you get\Nfor messing with Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! You really disappoint me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after you stole\Nour ship and ran off,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy didn't suspect you one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, he completely trusts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you trick someone like\Nthat with such an uncaring look?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I trust is money.\NThose who get fooled are the fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.07,0:16:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was\Nsupposed to go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are going to make my\Neight years of business meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the least I can do is\Nget rid of you by my own hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.28,0:17:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you've become a lot more\Npirate-like since you were last here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, get rid of me?!\NDon't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't underestimate\Nme if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.40,0:17:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay here, I'm dead for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.58,0:17:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoke Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard used a smoke bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surround him! Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like\Nsomething you'd think up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was my only choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami... How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die like a good little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Way to go, Nami!\N--Way to get revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's why you're a\Nleader of the Arlong Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Big Sis Nami k-killed Big Bro Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you wanted, right?\NTo die at sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami. I'm sorry for doubting you.\NYou're our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one reason\Nwhy I joined this group!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:19:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To buy Cocoyashi Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your part of the bargain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have the 100 million Berries soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather cut my belly open and die
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than break a promise\Nconcerning money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of man I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it, Arlong.\NYou know the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's one creepy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a truly great\Nwoman she's become!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A witch! She's really a witch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! Arlong Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't get tired, cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Big Bro Sanji's kicks\Nmust've really taken their toll!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Not that way!\NTo the left! That building!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I've come so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've endured eight whole\Nyears since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! As of today, this is your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your desk, your pens...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you'll need is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I endured it all this time... so I had\Nno other choice than to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's almost like we're flying!\N--Not "like"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are flying, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Landing successful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it! We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell... are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NWe're here to get Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you still not found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! And what about\NUsopp and Johnny?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's right! There's no time\Nto be loafing around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard's been caught by Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hurry before he's killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He was killed!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.42,0:22:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.93,0:22:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Usopp is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.27,0:22:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Big Sis Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.76,0:22:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I... a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:23:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:24:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami would never kill Usopp!\NWe're friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.98,0:24:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami-san! It's me!\NDo you remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.48,0:24:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Why are you here?!\N--To get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.42,0:24:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! Where's Usopp?!\N--Bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.22,0:24:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.72,0:24:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Get the hell out, outsiders!\NYou're an eyesore!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.66,0:24:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.99,0:24:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone's Gathered!\NUsopp Speaks the Truth About Nami"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.30,0:24:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.13,0:24:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
